{%- comment -%} Product Features Highlights Section {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="product-features">
  <h2 class="product-features__title">So much more than just a digital calendar</h2>
  <div class="product-features__grid">
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>Custom-Built Calendar</h3>
      <p>Connect Google, iCal, and Outlook calendars or add events directly. The whole family can see what's coming up.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>Unlimited Lists</h3>
      <p>From to-dos and grocery lists to private checklists, keep track of everything that has to get done.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>Customizable Routines</h3>
      <p>Kid-friendly icons, personalized imagery, and Streaks to encourage consistency and autonomy for kids of any age.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>Companion App</h3>
      <p>Stay organized and up to date from anywhere. Create routines, share calendars, and get notified on the go.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>AI-Powered Hearth Helper</h3>
      <p>Digitize and upload paper invites and calendars from your phone. Hearth Helper makes it effortless to keep your calendar up to date.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-feature">
      <h3>Unlimited Profiles</h3>
      <p>Provide access for your whole family, sitters, nannies, and grandparents. Everyone stays in sync.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.product-features {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  margin: 2rem 0;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
.product-features__title {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #183642;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.product-features__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
}
.product-feature h3 {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: #00c2b3;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.product-feature p {
  color: #183642;
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin: 0;
}
@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .product-features__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>

